<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, minimum-scale=1.0, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>Belleza Organica</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora" rel="stylesheet">

    <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #091f5d;
      background-color: white;
      margin: 0;
    }

    #main {
      padding: 5px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    #logo {
      width: 64px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin: 0 8px;
    }

    #logo-td {
      width: 80px
    }

    #header-title {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 1.3em;
    }

    #header-title span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.75em;
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    #header-table {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      table-layout: fixed;
      background-color: white;
    }

    .overflow-text {
      overflow: hidden;
      white-space: nowrap;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .oxxo-sub {
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 16px;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      color: black;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      max-width: 616px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .oxxo-sub h3 {
      color: #9e9e9e;
    }
    .oxxo-sub ol {
      list-style: decimal;
      margin-left: 20px;
    }
    .oxxo-sub li {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .opps-info {
      display: table;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .opps-amount {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      width: 60%;
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .opps-brand {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      width: 35%;
      padding-right: 16px;
    }
    .opps-brand img {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .box {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      overflow: hidden;
      will-change: height;
      background: rgb(224,224,224);
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .add-box {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      overflow: hidden;
      will-change: height;
      margin: 8px 0;
      max-width: 616px;
    }

    .ref-box {
      padding: 8px;
    }

    .order-table {
      margin-top: 20px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 650px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 3px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      text-align: left;
      background-color: white;
    }
    .order-table td {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 8px;
    }
    .order-table td img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 112px;
      min-width: 10px;
    }
    .order-table td:last-child {
      padding: 0;
    }
    .order-table th {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding: 16px 8px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .order-table th:last-child {
      padding-right: 16px;
    }
    .order-table i {
      color: #e53a3c;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .order-table-foot td {
      border: none;
      text-align: right;
      padding: 5px 5px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #616161;
    }
    .order-table-foot .foot-main {
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #091f5d;
      text-align: right;
      width: 50px;
    }

    .foot-main {
      padding-right: 8px !important;
    }

    .sub-text {
      color: #757575;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
    .sub-text.primary {
      color: #091f5d;
    }
    .sub-text.light {
      color: #337ab7;
    }

    .xs-td {
      display: table-cell;
      width: 65%;
    }

    .xs-span {
      display: block;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 8px 0;
      white-space: normal;
    }

    .sm-td {
      display: none;
    }

    .col-xs-hide {
      display: none;
    }

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <table id="header-table">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td id="logo-td">
            <img id="logo" src="https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/belleza-node/web/nyr_logo.jpg" alt="Neals Yard Mexico">
          </td>
          <td>
            <h1 id="header-title">
              Neal's Yard Remedies México
              <span>  Salud y Belleza Orgánica </span>
            </h1>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <div id="main">
      <h3 style="color: #FFC107;">En Espera de Pago</h3>
      <p style="font-weight: bold">
        Hola {{user.first_name}} {{user.last_name}},
        <br>
        Gracias por comprar nuestros productos. Cuando recibamos su pago, su pedido será enviado
      </p>

      <div class="oxxo-sub">
        <div class="opps-info">
          <div class="opps-brand"><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/conekta-examples/spei-payment-stub/master/demo/spei_brand.png" alt="SPEI"/></div>
          <div class="opps-amount">
            <h3>Monto a pagar</h3>
            <h2>${{formatNumber order.total}} MXN</h2>
            <p class="sub-text">Esto expira en 3 días</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>Clabe</h3>
          <h2 class="box ref-box">{{order.charges.payment_method.clabe}}</h2>
        </div>

        <h3>Instrucciones</h3>

        <ol>
					<li>Accede a tu banca en línea.</li>
					<li>Da de alta la CLABE en esta ficha. <strong>El banco deberá de ser STP</strong>.</li>
					<li>Realiza la transferencia correspondiente por la cantidad exacta en esta ficha, <strong>de lo contrario se rechazará el cargo</strong>.</li>
					<li>Al confirmar tu pago, el portal de tu banco generará un comprobante digital. <strong>En el podrás verificar que se haya realizado correctamente.</strong> Conserva este comprobante de pago.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="">

      </div>

      <table class='order-table'>
        <thead>
          <tr class="col-xs-hide">
            <th>Producto</th>
            <th>Descripción</th>
            <th>Precio</th>
            <th>Cantidad</th>
            <th class="overflow-text">Subtotal <span class="sub-text">Sin IVA</span></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          {{#each order.details}}
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img src="{{formatImageLink this.plu}}">
            </td>

            <td class="xs-td" colSpan="4">
              <span class="xs-span">
                {{this.name}}
              </span>

              <span class="xs-span">
                <span class="sub-text">Precio: </span>${{formatNumber this.price}}
              </span>

              <span class="xs-span">
                {{this.quantity}}
              </span>

              <span class="xs-span">
                <span class="sub-text">Subtotal: </span>${{formatNumber this.sub_total}}
              </span>
            </td>
          </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <table class='order-table' style="margin-top: 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr class="col-xs-hide">
            <th></th>
            <th></th>
            <th></th>
            <th></th>
            <th class="overflow-text"></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="border: none; padding: 0"></td>
            <td style="border: none; padding: 0"></td>
            <td style="border: none; padding: 0"></td>
            <td style="border: none; padding: 0"></td>
            <td style="border: none; padding: 0"></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>

        <tfoot class="order-table-foot">
          <tr>
            <td colSpan="4">Subtotal: </td>
            <td class="foot-main">${{formatNumber order.sub_total }}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colSpan="4">IVA:</td>
            <td class="foot-main">${{formatNumber order.iva_total }}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colSpan="4">Costo de Envío: </td>
            <td class="foot-main">${{formatNumber order.shipping_total }}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colSpan="4">Discount:</td>
            <td class="foot-main">-${{formatNumber order.discount_total }}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colSpan="4">Total:</td>
            <td class="foot-main">${{formatNumber order.total }}</td>
          </tr>
        </tfoot>
      </table>

      <div class="add-box overflow-text sub-text">
        <p>Dirección de Envío</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="overflow-text">
          {{order.shippingAddress.first_name}} {{order.shippingAddress.last_name}}
        </p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.shippingAddress.telephone}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.shippingAddress.street}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.shippingAddress.street2}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">
          {{order.shippingAddress.city}}, {{order.shippingAddress.state}}
        </p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.shippingAddress.zipcode}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.shippingAddress.country}}</p>
      </div>

      {{#if order.invoiceAddress}}
      <div class="add-box overflow-text sub-text">
        <p>Facturación</p>
        <p>{{order.razon_social}}</p>
        <p>{{order.rfc}}</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="overflow-text">
          {{order.invoiceAddress.first_name}} {{order.invoiceAddress.last_name}}
        </p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.invoiceAddress.telephone}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.invoiceAddress.street}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.invoiceAddress.street2}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">
          {{order.invoiceAddress.city}}, {{order.invoiceAddress.state}}
        </p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.invoiceAddress.zipcode}}</p>
        <p class="overflow-text">{{order.invoiceAddress.country}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
